text: Canlubang Industrial Estate, abbreviated as CIE, and also known as the Silangan Industrial Park is an industrial park in South Luzon, Philippines on Jose A. Yulo Blvd. It is in Cabuyao in the Laguna province. It is an addition to Silangan Industrial Park. It is 500 meters southeast in Canlubang, Calamba City.https://www.yellow-pages.ph/business/canlubang-industrial-estate-assn The industrial estate has a lot of factories outside of Metro Manila. ==References== Laguna
